    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/b6b65bcce10cef7945708ff0f9674e57.avif?t=1718012009\" width=608 height=69 /></span><br><br>Tell your kids this is how it happened.<br><br><u><strong><i>Fight the pandemic like a legend!</i></strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/109e457c9e1770ef1dc37164a8f42d72.poster.avif?t=1718012009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/109e457c9e1770ef1dc37164a8f42d72.webm?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/109e457c9e1770ef1dc37164a8f42d72.mp4?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Stop the virus from entering your home by all means, if it does enter... blow it into pieces.<br><br><u><i><strong>Get vaccinated!</strong></i></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/8ac8b87daa6f033fc369e1dd59deedae.poster.avif?t=1718012009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/8ac8b87daa6f033fc369e1dd59deedae.webm?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/8ac8b87daa6f033fc369e1dd59deedae.mp4?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Stay one step ahead of the deadly virus by getting your 46th booster shot.<br><br><u><strong><i>Kill every mutation!</i></strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/e099812103812505cf3c7184b2dc6943.poster.avif?t=1718012009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/e099812103812505cf3c7184b2dc6943.webm?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/e099812103812505cf3c7184b2dc6943.mp4?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>They just keep on coming... and you have to keep coming up with new ways to kill them. Slay hordes of viruses while listening to killer music. Experience a truly cathartic experience.<br><br><u><strong><i>Clean your chair.</i></strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/69505e14bef8477d3594cf8e610cf16e.poster.avif?t=1718012009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/69505e14bef8477d3594cf8e610cf16e.webm?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/69505e14bef8477d3594cf8e610cf16e.mp4?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Just do it!<br><br><u><strong><i>Save your country!</i></strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/d0d0b7bb7f78177697095f607d143289.poster.avif?t=1718012009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/d0d0b7bb7f78177697095f607d143289.webm?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/d0d0b7bb7f78177697095f607d143289.mp4?t=1718012009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Experience overwhelming national pride in this patriotic experience. Exterminate the mysterious source of the pandemic. Save your country. Avenge your grandparent. What are you waiting for? Go fight like a man and make your president proud!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814060/extras/f7d637b41d7cce334a180427170f6ca8.avif?t=1718012009\" width=608 height=290 /></span><br><br>Image used in header capsule/banner &quot;Man with surgical mask on white background with copy space&quot; was created  by Jernej Furman, distributed under Attribution 2.0 Generic (CC BY 2.0) creative commons license (  ) and was modified (changed) for the purposes<br>of this works promotional material (color graded, cropped and mixed with other elements).",
